# 🌍 Namma Ooru - Tourist Guide Booking System

## 📌 Project Description
Namma Ooru is a web application that helps users explore cities, find tourist places, and book local guides.

---

## 🚀 Live Demo
👉 https://nammaooru.netlify.app

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Backend: Spring Boot (Java)
- Database: MySQL

---

## ✨ Features
- User Registration & Login
- Explore Cities & Tourist Places
- Guide Booking System
- Responsive UI

---

## ⚠️ Note
Backend APIs are not deployed. This is a frontend demo.

